cuments: All India Permit, PUC, Vehicle Insurance, Fitness Certificate.</li><li>Valid commercial driving license of the driver.</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td><b>EMD / Bid Security:</b></td></tr><tr><td><ul><li>EMD Amount: Rs. 46,000/-</li><li>Mode of Payment: Online payment through the website http://www.mahatenders.gov.in.</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td><b>Other Points:</b></td></tr><tr><td><ul><li>The bidder should provide a detailed proposal on how to handle the project and upload all documents in लिफाफा क्रं.-1 (Technical Bid).</li><li>The bidder or his representatives should be present at the office of the Executive Engineer, Nandur Madmeshwar Irrigation Department, Vaijapur during the opening of the tender.</li><li>The bidder or his representatives should be present at the office of the Executive Engineer, Nandur Madmeshwar Irrigation Department, Vaijapur during the opening of the लिफाफा क्रं. 02 BOQ File.</li><li>Vehicle manager salary and allowances responsibility of private agency will be responsible.</li><li>Minimum One vehicle manager as assistant will be required for each vehicle.</li><li>The bidder or its members shouldn't have any relation with political parties or politicians.</li><li>Information regarding the works undertaken by the bidder, along with the required documents.</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td><b>Technical Evaluation Criteria (गुणदान):</b></td></tr><tr><td><ul><li>Experience of the bidder in providing vehicle arrangements to government/semi-government offices.<ul><li>5 years: 12 marks</li><li>5 to 8 years: 16 marks</li><li>More than 8 years: 20 marks</li></ul></li><li>Manpower available with the bidder for vehicle arrangement.<ul><li>Minimum 1 manpower: 12 marks</li><li>2 to 3 manpower: 16 marks</li><li>More than 3 manpower: 20 marks</li></ul></li><li>Stability of the bidder (local residence proof).: 20 marks</li><li>Turnover of the bidder in the last three years (certificate of the auditor).<ul><li>Minimum Rs. 36 Lakh: 12 marks</li><li>Rs. 36 Lakh to Rs. 50 Lakh: 16 marks</li><li>More than Rs. 50 Lakh: 20 marks</li></ul></li><li>Proposal on how to handle the project: 20 marks</li></ul></td></tr></table>","Checklist":"1. Scanned copy of the online payment receipt for blank e-tender form2. Scanned copy of the online payment receipt for EMD (Earnest Money Deposit)3. Technical Bid4. Shop Act License / Registration Certificate of the organization5. PAN card6. Aadhar card7. CA certificate for vehicle arrangement of minimum Rs. 30 Lakhs in last 3 years8. Declaration regarding acceptance of terms and conditions9. GST Registration Certificate10. GST Return for the last 2 years F.Y. 2023-24, 2024-25, 2025-2611. Self-declaration of not being blacklisted12. Receipt of payment of business tax for the year 2025-2613. Certificate of average annual turnover of Rs. 12 Lakhs for the last 3 years14. Income Tax Return and Balance Sheet for the last 3 years F.Y. 2023-24, 2024-25, 2025-2615. Certificate from Class-1 officer for satisfactory work completion16. List of required machinery/materials17. List of available manpower/employees18. Vehicle documents - All India Permit, PUC, Vehicle Insurance, Fitness Certificate19. Driver's valid commercial driving license20. Proposal21. Earnest Money Deposit22. DD from Nationalized Bank23. Certificate from CA for works of vehicle supply of minimum Rs 30 Lakhs in last 3 years24. निविदा धारक फर्मचे नाव (Name of tenderer firm)25. निविदा धारकांचे पुर्ण नाव (Full name of tenderers)26. पत्ता दुरध्वनी क्रमांक व ईमेल (Address, telephone number and email)27. शॉपॲक्ट लायसन्स / संस्थेचे नोंदणी प्रमाणपत्र (Shop Act License / Organization Registration Certificate)28. वाहनाचे कागदपत्रे- All India Permit, PUC, वाहनाचा विमा (Insurance), फिटनेस प्रमाणपत्र (Fitness Certificate) आणि पीयुसी (PUC), पॅन कार्ड व आधारकार्ड, चालकाचे वैध व्यावसायिक ड्रायव्हिंग लायसन्स (Vehicle documents - All India Permit, PUC, Vehicle Insurance, Fitness Certificate and PUC, PAN card and Aadhar card, Valid commercial driving license of the driver.)29. निविदा धारकाने मागील 3 वर्षात किमान 30 लाख रु पर्यंतची चहापान, अल्पोपहार व भोजन व्यवस्था पुरवठा केल्याचे कामे पार पाडले असल्याबाबत CA यांचे प्रमाणपत्र (Certificate from CA for having completed works of tea, refreshments and food supply of at least Rs. 30 lakhs in the last 3 years.)30. अटी व शर्तीच्या मान्यतेबाबत प्रतिज्ञापत्र (अटी सोबत जोडले आहे त्याच नमुन्यामध्ये असावे) (Declaration regarding acceptance of terms and conditions (should be in the same format as attached with the terms))31. GST प्रमाणपत्र रजिस्ट्रेशन (GST registration certificate)32. GST रिटर्न मागील २ वर्षाचे F.Y.2024-25,2025-26 (GST return for the last 2 years F.Y.2024-25,2025-26)33. काळ्या यादीत समाविष्ट नसल्याबाबतचे स्वयंघोषणापत्र (Self declaration of not being included in black list)34. सन 2025-26चा व्यवसाय कर भरणा केल्याबाबत पावती (Receipt of payment of business tax for the year 2025-26)35. निविदाधारकाच्या/संस्थेच्या मागील 3 वर्षात प्रति वार्षिक उलाढाल रु. 12 लाख असल्याचे प्राधिकरणाचे किंवा चार्टर्ड अकाटंट यांचे प्रमाणपत्र जोडणे आवश्यक राहील. (It is necessary to attach the certificate of the authority or Chartered Accountant stating that the annual turnover of the tenderer/organization for the last 3 years is Rs. 12 lakhs.)36. मागील 3 वर्षाचे F.Y.-2023-24.2024-25,2025-26 आयकर रिटर्न व अधिकृत Balance Sheet (Last 3 years F.Y.-2023-24.2024-25,2025-26 Income tax return and official Balance Sheet)37. यापूर्वी शासकीय कार्यक्रमात अशा प्रकारचे कामे समाधानकारक रित्या पार पाडले असल्याबाबत वर्ग-1 दर्जाच्या अधिकाऱ्याचे प्रमाणपत्र (Certificate from Class-1 officer for satisfactory completion of such works in earlier government programs)38. आवश्यक यंत्रसामग्री/साहित्य (Required machinery/materials)39. उपलब्ध मनुष्यबळ/कर्मचारी यांची यादी (List of available manpower/employees)40. गोदा ते नर्मदा - पुण्यश्लोक अहिल्यादेवी जलयात्रा करिता वाहन व्यवस्था पुरवठा मागणीनुसार विहित वेळेत करणेबाबतचे नियोजनाचे प्रस्ताव (Proposals for planning to supply vehicle system for Goda to Narmada - Punyashlok Ahilyadevi Jalyatra as per demand in stipulated time.)41. मागील तीन वर्षाचे टर्नओव्हर सर्टिफिकेट (सनदी लेखापाल यांनी प्रमाणीत केलेले) (Turnover certificate for the last three years (certified by the certified accountant))42. पुराव्यादाखल छायांकित प्रति जोडाव्यात (Provide photocopy for proof)"}],"StatusCode":200}